name: Turks and Taquitos
description: You find yourself waking up on the shore of a random island. How did I get here? What happened to the rest of the boat? Why am I so hungry? Well you have nothing to worry about, there's plenty of supplies on Turks and Taquitos for you to make a taco, you just have to ask the right people. It's never a bad time for TACO TIME!
